{"name":"Tamer","type":"class","img":"icons/creatures/abilities/cougar-pounce-stalk-black.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>As a tamer, you gain the following class features.</p><h3>Hit Points</h3><p><strong>Hit Dice:</strong> 1d8 per tamer level<br /><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level:</strong> 8 + your Constitution modifier<br /><strong>Hit Points at Higher Levels:</strong> 1d8 (or 5) + your Constitution modifier per tamer level after 1st</p><h3>Proficiencies</h3><p><strong>Armor:</strong> Light armour, medium armour, shields<br /><strong>Weapons:</strong> Simple weapons, nets<br /><strong>Tools:</strong> One type of artisan's tools or one musical instrument of your choice<br /><strong>Saving Throws:</strong> Constitution, Charisma<br /><strong>Skills:</strong> Choose two from Animal Handling, Insight, Medicine, Nature, Perception and Persuasion</p><h3>Equipment</h3><p>You start with the following equipment, in addition to the equipment granted by your background:</p><ul><li>(a) @Compendium[dnd5e.items.XmnlF5fgIO3tg6TG]{Scale Mail} or (b) @Compendium[dnd5e.items.WwdpHLXGX5r8uZu5]{Leather Armor}</li><li>A simple melee weapon, a @Compendium[dnd5e.items.aEiM49V8vWpWw7rU]{Net}, and a @Compendium[dnd5e.items.sSs3hSzkKBMNBgTs]{Shield}</li><li>A @Compendium[dnd5e.items.ddWvQRLmnnIS0eLF]{Light Crossbow} and @Compendium[dnd5e.items.SItCnYBqhzqBoaWG]{20 Bolts}</li><li>(a) a dungeoneer’s pack or (b) an explorer’s pack</li></ul><p>If you forgo this starting equipment, as well as the items offered by your background, you start with [[/r 5d4 * 10]] gp to buy your equipment.</p><h1>Tamer Advancement</h1><table><thead><tr><td>Level</td><td>Proficiency Bonus</td><td>Features</td></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1st</td><td>+2</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.loot-tavern-tamer.player-features.vxb9WMUG0a8ULpOX]{Pocket Familiar}, @UUID[Compendium.loot-tavern-tamer.player-features.u4DNY2OOkYtzoBJD]{Monster Trainer}, @UUID[Compendium.loot-tavern-tamer.player-features.ITFk6VDz5RQKcKQz]{Soul Bond}, @UUID[Compendium.loot-tavern-tamer.player-features.EQvxhLNXsIgB3Npp]{Tame Creature}</td></tr><tr><td>2nd</td><td>+2</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.loot-tavern-tamer.player-features.RdivmVc4XTEzPAWf]{Bolster}, @UUID[Compendium.loot-tavern-tamer.player-features.dNi6mQV8TiqR4N2i]{Psychic Bond}, @UUID[Compendium.loot-tavern-tamer.player-features.QDRVESmOU60b4ZyZ]{Spellcasting (Tamer)}</td></tr><tr><td>3rd</td><td>+2</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.loot-tavern-tamer.player-features.sCNafDEAbMJC5Zkp]{Pocket Family}, @UUID[Compendium.loot-tavern-tamer.player-features.yRbXZoT097oybRw0]{Training Paradigm}</td></tr><tr><td>4th</td><td>+2</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.classfeatures.s0Cc2zcX0JzIgam5]{Ability Score Improvement}</td></tr><tr><td>5th</td><td>+3</td><td>2nd Level Spell Slot, @UUID[Compendium.loot-tavern-tamer.player-features.apYHitRwCZo8Kqk8]{Multiattack (Tamer)}, @UUID[Compendium.loot-tavern-tamer.player-features.pTL6uKqEcLdPpWbk]{Malleable Presence}</td></tr><tr><td>6th</td><td>+3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.loot-tavern-tamer.player-features.RGJklDr1joQ3wBh8]{Alpha Strike}, @UUID[Compendium.loot-tavern-tamer.player-features.3UswntTHKvGMN5Eu]{Wilful Blows}</td></tr><tr><td>7th</td><td>+3</td><td>Pocket Family (2), Training Paradigm Feature</td></tr><tr><td>8th</td><td>+3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.classfeatures.s0Cc2zcX0JzIgam5]{Ability Score Improvement}</td></tr><tr><td>9th</td><td>+4</td><td>3rd Level Spell Slot</td></tr><tr><td>10th</td><td>+4</td><td>Training Paradigm Feature</td></tr><tr><td>11th</td><td>+4</td><td>Pocket Familiar (3)</td></tr><tr><td>12th</td><td>+4</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.classfeatures.s0Cc2zcX0JzIgam5]{Ability Score Improvement}</td></tr><tr><td>13th</td><td>+5</td><td>4th Level Spell Slot, @UUID[Compendium.loot-tavern-tamer.player-features.5hEfREjKZbHKb91M]{Switcheroo}</td></tr><tr><td>14th</td><td>+5</td><td>Training Paradigm Feature</td></tr><tr><td>15th</td><td>+5</td><td>Pocket Familiar (4)</td></tr><tr><td>16th</td><td>+5</td><td>@